{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvDecideGoal\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">cbvDecideGoal</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Attempt to close a goal of the form `decide P = true` by reducing only the LHS using `cbv`.\n\n- If the LHS reduces to `Bool.true`, the goal is closed successfully.\n- If the LHS reduces to `Bool.false`, throws a user-friendly error indicating the proposition is false.\n- Otherwise, throws a user-friendly error showing where the reduction got stuck.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvDecideGoal","kind":"def","line":328,"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvDecideGoal","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.lean#L328-L352"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvGoal\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">cbvGoal</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Reduce both sides of an equation goal. Tries the LHS first, then the RHS.\nUsed by the `cbv` tactic. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvGoal","kind":"def","line":321,"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvGoal","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.lean#L321-L326"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvGoalCore\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">cbvGoalCore</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">inv</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.false\">false</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Reduce one side of an equation goal. When `inv = false`, reduces the LHS;\nwhen `inv = true`, reduces the RHS. Returns `none` if the goal is closed,\nor a residual goal with the reduced side. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvGoalCore","kind":"def","line":284,"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvGoalCore","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.lean#L284-L319"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvEntry\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">cbvEntry</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/SimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Result\">Sym.Simp.Result</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Reduce a single expression. Unfolds reducibles, shares subterms, then runs the\nsimplifier with `cbvPre`/`cbvPost`. Used by `conv => cbv`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvEntry","kind":"def","line":274,"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbvEntry","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.lean#L274-L282"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbv.warning\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">warning</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/Options.html#Lean.Option\">Lean.Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbv.warning","kind":"opaque","line":94,"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.cbv.warning","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/Main.lean#L94-L97"}}],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Sym","Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.SimpM","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvEvalExt","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.ControlFlow","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.Opaque","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.TheoremsLookup","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.Util","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Refl"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.Main"}